LINUX METHOD

1) Go into the diretory where you hold your header_file, malloc_new.c file and yout main.c file using terminal.
2) run the following command
	->	gcc malloc_new.h malloc_new.c main.c -o mall
	->	./mall
**and you can edit the main.c file as you wish
